      public Product(String name, String measurementForm, int calories, int protein, int carbs, int fat)
      Constructor to initialize a Product object with specified attributes.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the product.
      measurementForm - The form of measurement (e.g., per unit, per 100g).
      calories - The number of calories in the product.
      protein - The amount of protein in grams.
      carbs - The amount of carbohydrates in grams.
      fat - The amount of fat in grams.
